  "synopsis": "Do you believe it? All encounters are destined, and two people who truly love each other will eventually come back to each other. Fettered by fate, Jiang Ling, the finless porpoise fairy, reunited with her lover Lin Sheng from her previous life across time and space. \n\nEven though they lost their memories, they still fell in love with each other again. However, obstacles come one after another. Can the two make up for their past regrets this time? Believe that those who love you will cross mountains and seas just to come for you.\n\n(Source: Bangumi, translated)",
